name: Non fungible human
description:
In "Non fungible human" an artificial intelligence of the future is represented that creates a tool that transforms humans into sculptures, manufacturing "non-fungible humans" as art that will be exhibited and exchanged with other artificial intelligences.

The animations created in this work (transformation from human to sculpture) have been created with artificial intelligence based on the works of the sculptor Pablo Serrano, born in Crivillén (Teruel) and one of the most important Spanish artists of the 20th century.
